  "text": "Berti et al. [CITATION_1] propose a disruptive business model producing new values and new markets by redefining the food supply chain. They introduce a digital food hub, an online marketplace, facilitating efficient connections among local food producers and consumers. Berti et al. [CITATION_2] argue that it is a sustainable business model as it increases the demand for the local food, and it also promotes healthy and sustainable food for the local communities. Berti et al. [CITATION_3] believe that this digital food hub, indeed, provides a strategic network across the food supply chain to coproduce socioenvironmental shared values.",
